Module gymmanager.gymproject3

Class Family

java.lang.Object
gymmanager.gymproject3.Member
gymmanager.gymproject3.Family
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Member>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Premium
public class Family extends Member implements Comparable<Member>
Used to create new Family objects that hold information for members with family tier membership. These objects can then be compared. Holds all member information, and number of guest passes. For family the max number of guest passes is 1.
Author:
Aaron Newland, Dylan Pina
